    IINC run 1
    BIPUSH 24
    ILOAD run
    ILOAD size_tbl
    IASTORE
    IINC run 1
    BIPUSH 8
    ILOAD run
    ILOAD size_tbl
    IASTORE
    IINC run 1
    BIPUSH 64
    ILOAD run
    ILOAD size_tbl
    IASTORE
